Since it seems more complicated than I thought, I went for the following solution: plot the discrete version of the continuous Fibonacci function, see for instance [here](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generalizations_of_Fibonacci_numbers). Any suggestions are surely still welcomed. 

